result.name: Shanghai Lu Yang Cun Restaurant

reviews.text: Price is reasonable. Food is ok. Nice harbour view.
One of my favorite Shanghainese cuisine in HK. The food is delicious with a homemade taste. Early birds may get a view of Causeway Bay.

Decent shanghai restaurant in Causeway Bay. A little bit pricy but the food is very nice. In other similar restaurants in HK, they may have one or two signature dishes that impress you. But in this place, the overall quality of all dishes is high. (And i like their signature chicken, not served in other restaurants). Good service and comfortable environment facing the sea view!
Good service, tasty food. Highly recommended.
Good place. Good window to see TST

result.name: 上海綠楊邨酒家

reviews.text: 位於世貿中心11樓，從銅鑼灣地鈇站D4出口，步行約6分鈡，交通方便。選了4人套餐，味道不錯，感覺份量有点少，特别是主食，胃口大的不夠喉，坐位舒適，方便茶聚傾計。
食物質素高，環境不錯，但價錢有點貴，走中檔路線！
吾欲擊汝肝，肺，心，胃，陽具(你全家都無能)望君嘗糞
Price is reasonable. Food is ok. Nice harbour view.
